OL,3,CHorse rider 'heartbroken' as
OL,4,Cthoroughbred dies after crash with
OL,5,Ctractor
OL,7,FA horse rider is pleading with drivers
OL,8,Fto be more careful after her
OL,9,Fthoroughbred had to be put down
OL,10,Ffollowing an incident involving a
OL,11,Ftractor.
OL,13,FAmy Hilton says she has been left
OL,14,Fheartbroken after her seven-year-old
OL,15,Fhorse Archie died after a crash on a
OL,16,Fquiet rural lane near Benenden, Kent,
OL,17,Fin February.
