OL,7,FMs Hilton says he was hit by a
OL,8,Ftractor's trailer that had been driven
OL,9,Ftoo close and too fast, so she wants
OL,10,Fto honour his memory by educating
OL,11,Fdrivers on how to approach horses on
OL,12,Fthe road.
OL,14,FAmy Hilton said: "I want drivers to
OL,15,Funderstand we're all in it together,
OL,16,Fall sharing the road and we need to
OL,17,Fall respect each other."
OL,19,F"The only option we had was to put him
OL,20,Fdown and that was tough because he was
OL,21,Fonly seven," Ms Hilton added.
