OL,3,CHorse rider 'heartbroken' as
OL,4,Cthoroughbred dies after crash with
OL,5,Ctractor
OL,7,F"Archie was my horse, and he was my
OL,8,Feverything. Horses aren't just a pet,
OL,9,Fthey're my whole life.
OL,11,F"I've put in everything to that horse
OL,12,Fand he just didn't deserve what
OL,13,Fhappened.
OL,15,FArchie was a thoroughbred cross, worth
OL,16,Ftens of thousands of pounds, and was
OL,17,Fabout to start the eventing season.
