OL,7,FArchie's mother had competed at a high
OL,8,Flevel but died giving birth to him, so
OL,9,FMs Hilton had bottle-fed Archie and
OL,10,Fspent five years training him.
OL,12,FA spokesperson for Kent Police said:
OL,13,F"At around 1.40pm on Tuesday 18
OL,14,FFebruary 2025 officers on patrol in
OL,15,FIden Green, near Benenden were flagged
OL,16,Fdown following a collision involving a
OL,17,Ftractor and a horse in Standen Street.
OL,19,F"The driver has since been identified
OL,20,Fand police say enquiries into the
OL,21,Fincident are ongoing.
